{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"92c2b13128","title":"血诗题衣","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"842c88f908","index":0,"year":1965,"month":3,"day":5,"articleId":"92c2b13128"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"c5892196e2","name":"林昭"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"61f4883a26","type":"title","text":"血诗题衣","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"923999157e","type":"authors","text":"北京大学林昭","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"3fc64d83f5","type":"subtitle","text":"血诗题衣  并跋","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"06c2cf6546","type":"paragraph","text":"双龙鏊战玄间黄，冤恨兆元付大江；蹈海鲁连今仍昔，横槊阿瞒慨当慷；只应社稷公黎庭，那许山河私帝王！汗愆神州赤子血，枉言正道是沧桑！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"8f8f11de38","type":"paragraph","text":"鼎钺罗前安足论，此身未惜叩天阁，桑麻奄绝中原黑，邦国轸调大野备，遗老长呤怀彼黍，逐臣痛哭赋招魂，治手从约何相负，请化阳春照银盆！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"490cf82fcf","type":"paragraph","text":"惊飙为我自天来，一曲清笳动地哀，墨菊素心侵夜夜，寒梅铁骨凛霜开，补成完宇苏民困，挽得狂澜免劫死；万木森然非佳兆，九州生气恃风雷。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"40a085da2d","type":"paragraph","text":"铁铸九州血泪滔，知君潜忏故对刀；百年基业于雄杰，万古云霄亦羽毛，愿释前仇归宿浦，更留余地容新荃，彼苍浩渺真无极，莫与天公试比高。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"e20dc229fd","type":"paragraph","text":"多情每笑钟离篇，爱国何因自呈身，巾帼从无儿女想，冕梳合与江山亲，茹冰苦志应穿石，守玉清操岂染尘，牵惜令名全圣德，贞娥匪比思夫人！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"3961243650","type":"paragraph","text":"永夜沉呤彻骨寒，瑶琴寂寞对谁弹，心存得失崇朝计，情怯是非来日难！怨毒遍栽根颇固，虎狼近伺意何闲，英雄暮年要深省，还祝前途十八滩！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"ddb4a0e6e6","type":"paragraph","text":"虚名实祸误苍生，底事猖狂好谈兵，罪已布公称大  ，归仁谢谤见真明；舆论士气必张护，民权世潮毋玩轻，天道无亲常与喜，休将耕耘问收成！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"c325d617d8","type":"paragraph","text":"李洪三世悼终年，历劫再来日未眠，伐骨亲仁先复礼，洗心偃武习修文；众生堪念当离魔，昊帝垂怜犹侍君。宝箴迷得迅受渡，好成正果上青云！","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"b6a3b04ec3","type":"paragraph","text":"东海沧波万顷愁，狐死兔龠恨悠悠，悲亲位具难安魄，媳我项存未断头！桑梓兴荣便是酬，邦家丰乐更何求，微明不邀宸聪虑，一腔沸血烛天流！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"10e8acba12","type":"paragraph","text":"无题九章，以当绝命，自伤身世，更痛家国。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"ca1eceb259","type":"paragraph","text":"殉道有志，弘道无得，肝肠百回，泪尽继血。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"614df7b18d","type":"paragraph","text":"苟延为公，尽命气节，后事再来，海天空阔。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"2ed64dccbf","type":"paragraph","text":"瑶琴韵断，悲笳声咽，昊帝灵爽，瞵儿清烈。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"bdae4b8f68","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九六五年三月五日要昭自题于狱中","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"75c118e4ce","type":"paragraph","text":"残喘赘疣，夙愿取义，敢谓成仁，自云知耻。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"b98a9781ae","type":"paragraph","text":"立身敦品，千秋清仪，生也何欢，大节正气。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"6bef1304ac","type":"paragraph","text":"三军罢帅，匹夫励志，读圣贤书，所学付事。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"0453d7d441","type":"paragraph","text":"日月经天，江河在地，君王不谅，有死而已！","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"93fd996636","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九六五年三月七日再题","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"},{"id":"21fc8ff26e","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《林昭文抄》，甘粹先生2000年7月11日抄本。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128"}],"page":{"id":"a86fb28686","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"92c2b13128","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}